To reduce diarrhea from the body and other fluxes.

Take 3 ounces each of urine of a healthy man, fine ashes of turkey oak and yellow litharge and mix them and make little balls of it and dry them in the shade. When you wish to use them, mix them with plantain juice, one or two each time, and put this warm on the navel in the evening when you go to sleep and soon it will restrain the body so you will not go too much, and soon you will be cured.

